='''distance'''=

<span style="font-size:110%">'''Description'''</span><br>
this function create an image where each pixel value correspond between the distance of that pixel to the closest background object in the input image

<span style="font-size:110%">'''Signature'''</span><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<code>outputImage = cip.distance(inputImage*, threshold, pixelSize)</code>

